eu.slipo.athenarc.triplegeo.utils

Class BatchReverseConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.slipo.athenarc.triplegeo.utils.BatchReverseConverter

  • public class BatchReverseConverter
extends Object
    Recreates a disk-based RDF graph and extracts its contents through a user-specified SELECT query in SPARQL. Results can be written to a typical geographical files (currently supported: CSV and ESRI Shapefiles). Attribute names in the SELECT query will become the column names in the resulting files.
    Version:
    1.9
    Author:
    Kostas Patroumpas
